# Optional public-flow helpers
# Use `npm run prepare:public -- --config-only` after a public deployment to sync chainId and addresses into .trustcommit/config.json.
# Use `npm run prepare:public` to mint mock tokens, register the executor agent, fund stake, and rotate the execution wallet on a public testnet.
# Use `npm run public:flow -- --mode submit` or `--mode dispute` to generate public receipts and an exported review bundle.
